I uploaded a chart listing three of Read's scripts: Shavian,
Quickscript, and ReadScript. The chart was originally developed by
Kingsley Read's daughter for an exhibition. The typography leaves a
little to be desired but the side by side relationships and key
words make of the scripts a little easier to grasp. Particularly
urge, err, and array.

Regards,

Steve
